<div type="translation" source="bib:Hultzsch1899_01">
	
	<p n="1">Hail! Prosperity! On the 122nd day of the 17th year <supplied reason="subaudible">of the reign</supplied> of king Rājakesarivarman,——we, the great assembly of Śrī-Vikramābharaṇa-caturveēdimaṅgalam,——including the great men elected for this year, the great <foreign>bhaṭṭa</foreign>s elected for <supplied reason="subaudible">the supervision of</supplied> the tank, and <supplied reason="subaudible">all other</supplied> distinguished men,——being assembled on this day in the Puvaṉimāṇikka-Viṣṇugr̥ham in our village, •••••</p>
</div>
	
<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
								
	<p n="1">Prosperity! Fortune!</p>
		
</div>
